data.description: Country Living at its Best. Ranch Style home that sits on 39+ acres. Open and Inviting Floor Plan. Delightful Living room with woodstove and pellet stove easy access to back deck. Spacious Kitchen with lots of cabinets and counter space. Comfortable and relaxing bedrooms. This home is truely a must see.
data.whatILove: Views are amazing and house sits in the middle of pastures no close neighbors. I’ve loved living here since day 1!  Very peaceful and easy access! Very little dirt roads!  No covenants and great community.  I have always had plenty of space to ride my horses it is a Nice sized horse property and small arena.  Fenced and cross fenced lots of hydrants for the livestock.  Barn and lean too and windbreak.  The views here are absolutely amazing.  The house has Tons of room and storage with high ceilings and super unique home.  Only 5 miles south of town and 5 separate pastures!  Tons of room to grow out here!
